{"problem": "Find $\\begin{pmatrix} 3 \\\\ -7 \\end{pmatrix} + \\begin{pmatrix} -6 \\\\ 11 \\end{pmatrix}.$", "solution": "We have that\n\\[\\begin{pmatrix} 3 \\\\ -7 \\end{pmatrix} + \\begin{pmatrix} -6 \\\\ 11 \\end{pmatrix} = \\begin{pmatrix} 3 + (-6) \\\\ (-7) + 11 \\end{pmatrix} = \\boxed{\\begin{pmatrix} -3 \\\\ 4 \\end{pmatrix}}.\\]"}